      "role": "user",
      "content": "but there's nobody to talk to. my parents dont get it and my friends... they're probably part of it or just watching it happen. it feels like the whole world is just one giant room of people pointing at me. there's no point in trying to fix it when everyone has already decided who i am. it's just constant. i just feel so heavy all the time.",
